net.hudup.core.data.ctx

Class ContextValueList

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.data.ctx.ContextValueList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class ContextValueList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is the list of ContextValue (s). It contains an internal variable list referred to this list. It provides utility methods for processing such list. Note, ContextValue represents a value of context template. A context represented by Context is composed of context template represented by ContextTemplate and context value represented by ContextValue.
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
